{"tid":113941,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"87%球迷希望艾歷尼取代雲加 成為阿仙奴新領隊！","createTime":"2017-02-09T11:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T16:22:15.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03f1ccbef5241862bed8f13186c7e3b8c8c3af72","tid":113941,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"近來關於雲加會離開阿仙奴的傳聞不絕於耳，早前英國媒體熱炒阿仙奴想要邀請祖雲達斯主帥艾歷尼接班雲加執教，對此艾歷尼本人做出了回應。頗為有趣的是，艾歷尼沒有否認執教阿仙奴的可能，反而和媒體打起了太極。<br />\n<br />\n在接受Mediaset Premium的採訪時，艾歷尼被問到執教阿仙奴的傳聞時回應：&ldquo;我不會否認或者宣布任何事情。我現在和球會同步，現在我們必須專注於贏球。這個賽季，媒體總是說我會離開，即便我們一切順利的時候也是如此。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯經理馬路達在接受采訪時談及艾歷尼的未來時則說：&ldquo;我們和艾歷尼還有合同，除此之外，我認為我們還有很多偉大的目標需要一切去征服，我們的關係也非常好。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　值得玩味的是，無論是艾歷尼還是馬路達都沒有正面回應或者否認有關阿仙奴的傳聞。英國媒體甚至打趣稱，艾歷尼這樣的的回應只是在給傳聞加料而已。不過可以確定的一點是，英國球迷對於艾歷尼取代雲加倒是比較期待，《鏡報》的球迷調查顯示，有多達87%參與調查的球迷認為阿仙奴應該用艾歷尼取代雲加。"},{"pid":"840d5858c5b1c3fdecd59ec9e5c37a170b5fe54e","tid":113941,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:30:39.000Z","msg":"87<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雲加係阿妓g柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00391cd3eff173b5c666df74388ee2fa2338686","tid":113941,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>87<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雲加係阿妓g柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無雲加就無阿仙奴"},{"pid":"f4bf9ca423cb7b276961a5f05d7dc51004bd1478","tid":113941,"uid":67331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"迷雲黨的我表示，爺爺係時候退休享下清福<br />\n咁多年排第四辛苦晒<br />\n冇雲加連第四都冇"},{"pid":"c4a32ef85eea662e280f980c1479910115da3533","tid":113941,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>87<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雲加係阿妓g柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無雲加就無阿仙奴</blockquote><br />\n雲加是阿記的紅太陽"},{"pid":"365d5673cb2b73564adf315f0ee4874ebe6e775c","tid":113941,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"走啦死佬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218c33cee31fec0256f07371c7a1caa1e7e918c0","tid":113941,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"有咩球迷就咩球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵埋件垃圾教<br />\n好心比d大志啦<br />\n都係雲加好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19a2ed3d8bf81781f91dc8cc53f51cb2bf3a768","tid":113941,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"換雲膠唔緊要<br />\n都唔好搵屌帥吖"},{"pid":"e88aded83f6937bdf5a96539329bc05792e75504","tid":113941,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"換屌帥做乜鳩"},{"pid":"abb9eb9159aed9391584fa492b3c07f8b79726c6","tid":113941,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩球迷就咩球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵埋件垃圾教<br />\n好心比d大志啦<br />\n都係雲加好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTrump反雲lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c48b8c97cdad0dc3888bd74c9fa87eb2ad22685","tid":113941,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"阿狗會後悔"},{"pid":"3b20019ea236a1d7de4cb288efc757c340db7160","tid":113941,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"玩留<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/